Infineon (Quest Global) Interview Questions

1) Asked about the LDO and other projects I previously did and told to explain the LDO project in detail.
2) 5T Differential amplifier, asked the design process and sizing of each transistor
3) Asked to explain the Buck converter circuit (basic one)
4) A 5V pulse is given to a C-R ckt (Differentiator). Draw the output voltage (taken across R)
5) Write LDO model in SV-RNM.
6) Explain the Flash ADC project I did. What were the test cases.
